|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([SearchPhrase@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                               |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1))]                                  |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                      |
|               |                 CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                           |
|               |                   FilterExec: URL@0 LIKE %google% AND SearchPhrase@1 !=                                                                               |
